[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about how the task only tests without compilation or running, but could external workflows generate necessary metadata? In the reachability repo, it seems I should test natively with the existing metadata and no agent involved. 
[thinking] 
[thinking] If the test only uses serialization of java.util.Properties, does that mean no additional configuration is needed? Since native images support serialization, all classes need to be listed in the serialization config. Maybe I should look into existing tests related to serialization to clarify.
[thinking] 
